<p>A custom plugin Iâ€™ve created to integrate the awesome image_optim tool with Jekyll so that all of your images will be losslessly optimized.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Custom <a href="https://github.com/chrisanthropic/image_optim-jekyll-plugin">image_optim</a> plugin will optimize all images in the /images folder and any subdirectories
